articles.title: Netflix rolls out mobile games to users in select European markets - TODAYonline
articles.description: Netflix has bought video game creator Night School Studio and rolled out five mobile gaming titles in select European markets, the company said on Tuesday, as it looks to diversify revenue sources amid intensifying competition in the streaming space.
